<section id="deploy-section" class="card">
    <div class="section-header">
        <div>
            <h2 class="play-mode-title">Deploy Smart Contract</h2>
            <h2 class="info-mode-title" style="display: none;">How to deploy a smart contract</h2>
        </div>
        <img
                src="/assets/images/icon-question.png"
                alt="mode switch"
                class="mode-switch-icon"
        />
    </div>
    <div class="play-mode slide-toggle open">
        <form id="deployContractForm" class="todo-form">
            <textarea
                    id="bytecodeInput"
                    rows="8"
                    style="width: 100%;"
                    placeholder="Paste your contract bytecode here"
            ></textarea>
            <button
                    type="submit"
                    class="btn btn-primary"
                    id="deployContractBtn"
            >
                Deploy Contract
            </button>
        </form>
        <div id="deploy-status"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-mode slide-toggle">
        <div class="info-mode-title" style="display: none;">
            <h2>How to deploy a smart contract</h2>
        </div>
        <p>This uses Overledger's <code>deployments/smart-contracts</code> prepare‐sign‐execute flow.
            We only handle contracts that do not require constructor parameters.</p>
    </div>
</section>
